						<summary>

						<p>Fragment lying near the house of Tirakaṇṇa Akkasāli.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">10th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It seems to refer to a person by name Guṇḍa. Details of this fragmentary record are lost. In the date portion only Śaka [9 • •] • • • • ba. 6 Monday can be made out. It is in characters of the 10th century A.D.</p>						

